com.cyc.baseclient

Class CycObjectLibraryLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.baseclient.CycObjectLibraryLoader
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    KBObjectLibraryLoader

    public class CycObjectLibraryLoader
extends Object
    This class locates and loads classes annotated as CycObjectLibrary, and provides methods to access their fields. This is useful for verifying that a Cyc server's KB meets your code's requirements.
